      "summary": "Built the .dashboard/ refresher (Node stdlib, no deps), GitHub Actions workflow, public deeni-dashboard scaffold, password-gated Linear-style HTML, alert engine, and STATUS.md generator. Plan in DASHBOARD_PLAN.md. Awaiting first run after Phase 0 token setup."
